<font size="-1">
<ul>
	<li>Awarded the Hans Fallada Prize
	<li>Based on the film <i>Sonnenallee</i>
	<li>Thomas Brussig and Leander Hau&szlig;mann were awarded the Drehbuchpreis der Bundesregierung (Screenplay Prize of the Federal Government) for their script to <i>Sonnenallee</i>
	<li><i>Am k&uuml;rzeren Ende der Sonnenallee</i> has not yet been translated into English
</ul>
