<p>
<font size="+1">Our Assessment:</font>
<br>
<blockquote>
<font size="+1" color="#ff0000">A-</font> : gentle lampoon of East Berlin life in the shadow of the Berlin Wall
</blockquote>
</p>
<p align=center><font size="-1">See <a href="#ours">our review</a> for fuller assessment.</font>
</p>

